StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetAllCoun.es]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body: AS BEGIN SELECT c.[StateCode] ,s.[Name] AS [StateName] ,c.[Code] ,c.[Name] FROM [MCRISS].[USMC].[vwCoun.es] c INNER JOIN [MCRISS].[USMC].[vwStatesWithTerritories] s ON c.StateCode = s.Code ORDER BY StateCode, Code END
